ca.ualberta.cs.shinyexpensetracker.models

Class Model<M extends Model<M>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.shinyexpensetracker.models.Model<M>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - The child class itself (required for IView usage).
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Coordinate, Destination, ExpenseClaim, ExpenseClaimList, ExpenseItem, Tag, TagList

    public abstract class Model<M extends Model<M>>
extends Object
    Base class for domain model classes. Allows management of associated views (adding/removing/notifying of updates). NOTE: when extending this class, you MUST provide the same class to as the class itself. For example: class Chair extends Model {} Source: http://stackoverflow.com/a/20933658/14064
